ult creature not only because of his professional ambition and social transgression, but also because of his intrusion into the domestic space and into the lives of others, especially women.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / General.2bisacsh  aGentleman.  amisogyny.  astereotype.  atransgression.0 cEPUBz97831107545990 cprintz978311075270040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311075450640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110754506423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110754506.jpg  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LAEC  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA18STMEE  aPDA5EBK